HEADWORD: Overflowing
<hw>O`ver*flow"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An overflow;
that which overflows; exuberance; copiousness.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He was ready to bestow the <qex>overflowings</qex> of his full
mind on anybody who would start a subject.</q>
<rj><qau>Macaulay.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Overflowingly</ent>⟦br⟧
